snippet.title: Rocket League Season 1 Trailer 2020
snippet.description:
Gear up for Season 1 in Rocket League! It all starts on September 23 when Rocket League goes free to play! Read more details at https://www.rocketleague.com/seasons/season-1/

Get the new Rocket Pass and unlock 70+ Tiers of items with Rocket Pass Premium, including the latest car, Harbinger. Face off in free Competitive Tournaments and earn Tournament Credits to unlock new items. Complete game-wide Weekly and Season Challenges to expand your inventory and earn XP. Climb the new Competitive Ranks and see if you can get all the way to Supersonic Legend.

It all starts with Season 1! Download and play Rocket League for free on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and Epic Games Store on September 23! TAKE. YOUR. SHOT.

#RocketLeagueFreeToPlay #DownloadRocketLeague #TakeYourShot
